Deployment details
--------------------------------------
1. up mongoDB
2. build the project -> mvn clean install
3. \smartSMS\smart-sms\modules\app-types\target --> copy app-ui.war
4. paste it to C:\Program Files\apache-tomcat-7.0.40\webapps

